    <div class="main review-item" id="1324433">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324433/" class="title-link">堆砌史料，泛泛而谈</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1324433"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fredan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2128753-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fredan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">fredan</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-12"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-12 13:58:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1324433_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很令人失望的一本书，本来是很容易发挥的一个题目。写得很泛泛，把人尽皆知的一些事用生硬的语言阐述出来，看了令人昏昏欲睡，像教科书，没有什么令人印象深刻的地方。之前在网上暂存架上还保存了该作者的一些其他书，翻看这本书后都清掉了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324433/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
